data.description: ***BRING BACK UP CONTRACT*** Make this lake front property your new home! Location is perfect to zip to work - hospitals, downtown or FSU. If you are working remote set up in the large sunroom to take in the unobstructed view of the lake. Master bedroom down, potential 6 bedrooms, separate dining & open floor plan. Inside utility/laundry room. Roof only 9 years pls, granite counter tops, real wood floors, new back deck & recently soft washed whole house. Lots of great amenities near by: Trader Joe’s, Fresh Market, shopping, restaurants & i-10. A-Rated school zones. Potential 6 bedrooms.
